<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Room Unavailability Notification</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; padding: 20px;">
        <h2 style="color: #333;">Room Unavailability Notification for Syphax Hotel</h2>
        <p>Dear {{ Fullname }}</p>
        <p>Unfortunately, the requested room is currently unavailable for reservation at Syphax Hotel:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Requested Room: {{ roomDoor }}</li>
            <li>Floor Number: {{ floor }}</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We apologize for the inconvenience. Please consider suggesting alternative rooms or contact the user to discuss other available options.</p>
        <p>Thank you,<br>
        {{ hotelName }} Dashboard</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
